=================
clReflect Authors
=================

Don Williamson (https://bitbucket.org/dwilliamson)
	Primary author and project owner.

Xuejie Xiao (https://bitbucket.org/xxuejie)
	64-bit, MacOSX/Linux/GCC port, CMake build enhancements on multiple platforms.

Rui Figueira (https://bitbucket.org/ruifig)
	Multiple inheritance support, bug fixing and Visual Studio debug helpers.

Paul Holden (https://bitbucket.org/hulkholden)
	Initial CMake build port.
